00:05.310 --> 00:06.520
<b>Kurome...</b>

00:06.900 --> 00:11.650
<b>Unlike you, I joined the military because I admired them.</b>

00:12.450 --> 00:14.280
<b>I owe my life to a naval officer.</b>

00:14.910 --> 00:17.030
<b>He was the man I wanted to be.</b>

00:17.450 --> 00:22.960
<b>A soldier's duty is to protect their country and its people with weapon in hand.</b>

00:23.790 --> 00:26.170
<b>I was able to become a soldier,</b>

00:26.960 --> 00:29.250
<b>but just what am I protecting right now?</b>

00:38.510 --> 00:41.520
Kurome's

00:38.510 --> 00:41.520
Snacks

00:45.140 --> 00:47.310
<b>So only four of us are left.</b>

00:48.690 --> 00:49.820
