00:49.820 --> 00:51.190
<b>This place feels a lot emptier.</b>

00:51.190 --> 00:53.070
<b>It does.</b>

00:53.070 --> 00:54.900
<b>What'll we do, Tatsumi?</b>

00:54.900 --> 00:58.200
<b>After this is over, we'll be on the streets.</b>

00:58.200 --> 01:03.710
<b>You're the one who dragged me into this in the first place!</b>

01:03.710 --> 01:07.250
<b>Then one thing lead to another and 
before I knew it, I was in neck-deep.</b>

01:07.250 --> 01:09.000
<b>Is that how it went?</b>

01:09.710 --> 01:13.970
<b>Well, it's only right for a lady to take responsibility, you know?</b>

01:14.590 --> 01:16.510
<b>N-No thanks!</b>

01:16.510 --> 01:19.850
<b>Besides, a world with no need for assassins is a good thing!</b>

01:19.850 --> 01:21.310
<b>That's true.</b>

01:21.720 --> 01:24.350
<b>Well, why don't we join a traveling circus together?</b>

01:24.350 --> 01:25.100
<b>Sounds good.</b>

01:25.100 --> 01:26.520
<b>Like hell!</b>

01:27.020 --> 01:29.150
<b>Thank you all for your hard work.</b>

01:29.150 --> 01:32.650
<b>Hey, don't act like this is the last time we'll ever see each other.</b>

01:32.980 --> 01:36.650
<b>Whether we reunite in the future is up to all of you.</b>

01:36.650 --> 01:38.530
<b>Well said.</b>

01:38.530 --> 01:41.530
<b>We're not gonna go down that easily.</b>

01:41.530 --> 01:42.490
<b>Yeah.</b>

01:42.490 --> 01:43.330
<b>You too, Tatsumi.</b>

01:43.330 --> 01:45.290
<b>Yeah, of course.</b>

01:46.660 --> 01:47.580
<b>Very well.</b>

01:48.000 --> 01:49.830
<b>This is Night Raid's final mission.</b>

01:50.250 --> 01:52.210
<b>Eradicate the corruption at its source.</b>

01:52.210 --> 01:54.300
<b>Take down Prime Minister Honest.</b>

01:58.890 --> 02:00.720
<b>You'd better come back alive.</b>

02:00.720 --> 02:03.100
<b>Yeah. I promise.</b>

