<b><i>You have to kill the prime minister within that time.</i></b>

03:47.950 --> 03:49.540
<b>Comrades!</b>

03:49.540 --> 03:54.500
<b>Today, we will overthrow this empire and begin anew!</b>

03:54.500 --> 03:58.460
<b>We will bring down the corrupt government with our own hands and create a nation</b>

03:58.460 --> 04:00.340
<b>where citizens can live peacefully!</b>

04:00.340 --> 04:02.590
<b>Yeah!</b>

04:05.600 --> 04:06.640
<b><i>I'm counting on you.</i></b>

04:10.350 --> 04:11.680
<b>Bingo!</b>

04:11.680 --> 04:13.690
<b>Palace security's light, just as we thought.</b>

04:14.060 --> 04:16.230
<b>The interior's just as Lubb mapped it.</b>

04:16.230 --> 04:17.690
<b>Good work.</b>

04:24.450 --> 04:26.160
<b>Night Raid!</b>

04:26.570 --> 04:28.700
<b>We don't wish to kill any more than necessary.</b>

04:29.120 --> 04:30.790
<b>Those who aren't prepared to die should leave.</b>

04:31.120 --> 04:32.370
<b>That isn't an option!</b>

04:32.790 --> 04:35.790
<b>It figures that the guards here are more determined.</b>

04:36.880 --> 04:38.250
<b>We've got no choice but to kill them.</b>

04:41.300 --> 04:43.510
<b>These three are too much for you.</b>

04:43.510 --> 04:45.050
<b>Please stand down.</b>

04:47.300 --> 04:48.810
<b>One of the Jaegers...</b>

04:48.810 --> 04:49.560
<b>Run!</b>

04:50.220 --> 04:51.890
<b>It's been a while.</b>

04:51.890 --> 04:54.060
<b>You remember me, Tatsumi?</b>

04:54.060 --> 04:56.400
<b>I don't suppose you'd let us through.</b>

04:57.060 --> 04:58.060
<b>No chance, right?</b>

04:59.150 --> 05:00.270
<b>None.</b>

05:00.270 --> 05:03.280
<b>When I take on a job, I see it through to the end.</b>

05:03.280 --> 05:06.110
<b>Even if it's the wrong thing to do?</b>

05:06.110 --> 05:10.540
<b>What is "right" and "wrong" 
is a question for future historians.</b>

05:11.330 --> 05:13.330
<b>There's no need for the rest of you to lose your lives.</b>

05:13.330 --> 05:14.290
<b>Please leave us.</b>

05:14.290 --> 05:15.370
<b>Huh?</b>

05:15.370 --> 05:16.170
<b>It's fine.</b>

05:16.580 --> 05:17.920
<b>In fact,</b>

05:18.500 --> 05:19.840
<b>you'd only be in the way.</b>

05:23.170 --> 05:23.710
<b>He's coming!</b>

05:26.630 --> 05:29.010
<b>So that's his Imperial Relic.</b>

05:29.760 --> 05:33.140
<b>What you say is true.</b>

05:33.140 --> 05:35.180
<b>The empire is completely degenerate.</b>

05:35.850 --> 05:37.900
<b>The current regime is sure to collapse.</b>

05:38.230 --> 05:40.400
<b>If you know that, why do you stand in our way?</b>

05:40.730 --> 05:43.650
<b>Your methods involve too much bloodshed.</b>

05:43.650 --> 05:45.280
<b>How can you lecture us like this?!</b>

05:45.280 --> 05:47.570
<b>I was once a teacher, you know.</b>

05:47.570 --> 05:48.160
<b>Huh?</b>

05:48.160 --> 05:50.620
<b>Why would someone like you join the Jaegers?</b>

05:51.160 --> 05:56.080
<b>Back in my hometown, my students 
were abducted and killed by bandits.</b>

05:56.790 --> 06:00.380
<b>However, the empire didn't deem it a crime.</b>

06:01.090 --> 06:03.460
<b>My village was very poor, after all.</b>

06:03.460 --> 06:06.800
<b>They were abandoned by those in charge.</b>

06:06.800 --> 06:08.630
<b>I never knew you had such a past.</b>

06:08.630 --> 06:12.890
<b>And that's why I bear a grudge against the empire.</b>

06:14.100 --> 06:15.350
<b>That so?</b>

06:15.350 --> 06:17.640
<b>Then why'd you side with them?</b>

06:17.640 --> 06:19.060
<b>Why aren't you with us?!</b>

06:20.560 --> 06:22.570
<b>I wanted to do things my way.</b>

06:22.570 --> 06:25.570
<b>To change the empire from within.</b>

06:25.570 --> 06:29.660
<b>But then you lot went and started a violent rebellion!</b>

06:30.280 --> 06:31.700
<b>You're a real pain to argue with.</b>

06:31.700 --> 06:34.580
<b>I'll let my fists do the talking!</b>

06:38.370 --> 06:39.790
<b>Akame! Tatsumi!</b>

06:39.790 --> 06:41.210
<b>Leave him to me!</b>

06:41.210 --> 06:42.130
<b>Leone!</b>

06:42.670 --> 06:45.130
<b>We can't all be held up here, right?</b>

06:45.130 --> 06:46.590
<b>I'll be fine! Go!</b>

06:47.170 --> 06:49.130
<b>Don't you dare die on us!</b>

06:51.640 --> 06:55.260
<b>Hey, before you kill the prime minister, 
let me get a punch in, okay?</b>

06:56.180 --> 06:58.680
<b>That said, I'll finish you off now!</b>

06:59.770 --> 07:03.650
<b>It's nothing personal, but your fate 
was sealed once you chose their side!</b>

07:03.650 --> 07:05.520
<b>Say your prayers, teacher!</b>

07:11.570 --> 07:12.570
<b>Seriously?</b>

07:13.030 --> 07:15.660
<b>My hidden ability: Divine Wings.</b>

07:15.660 --> 07:19.290
<b>It seems you grossly underestimated my close-quarters combat skill.</b>

07:20.040 --> 07:21.370
<b><i>Crap...</i></b>

07:22.040 --> 07:24.380
<b>Prime Minister, how is the battlefront?</b>

07:24.380 --> 07:26.750
<b>Unfavorable.</b>

07:26.750 --> 07:33.510
<b>The rebels fight with passion and idealism, 
and our forces wither before them.</b>

07:33.510 --> 07:35.180
<b>A rebellion...</b>

07:35.180 --> 07:37.140
<b>Have I governed them so poorly?</b>

07:37.140 --> 07:38.140
<b>Not at all.</b>

07:38.140 --> 07:40.140
<b>Even after your parents passed,</b>

07:40.140 --> 07:43.770
<b>you've upheld your position as emperor splendidly.</b>

07:43.770 --> 07:46.190
<b>And I've watched over you this whole time.</b>

07:46.190 --> 07:48.780
<b>Rest assured, you have not erred.</b>

07:48.780 --> 07:51.360
<b>Th-That's true.</b>

07:51.360 --> 07:53.410
<b>You've always been by my side.</b>

07:54.620 --> 07:58.540
<b>Your Excellency, the citizens have been captivated by nonsense—</b>

07:58.540 --> 08:01.790
<b>a nonsense they call rebellion.</b>

08:02.210 --> 08:05.540
<b>You must make an example of these traitors.</b>

08:05.540 --> 08:07.500
<b>Yes, blood will be spilled,</b>

08:07.960 --> 08:11.380
<b>but an emperor must be austere!</b>

08:11.380 --> 08:15.850
<b>This frivolous rebellion will settle down once you demonstrate your authority.</b>

08:15.850 --> 08:17.350
<b>Now, let us be on our way.</b>

08:26.610 --> 08:29.070
<b><i>Somehow, I made it.</i></b>

08:29.070 --> 08:30.480
<b>A rebel!</b>

08:31.780 --> 08:33.700
<b>Night Raid...</b>

08:33.700 --> 08:36.450
<b>What were the palace guards doing?</b>

08:40.620 --> 08:42.710
<b>No further bodyguards of note.</b>

08:44.120 --> 08:46.630
<b>The target is Prime Minister Honest.</b>

08:47.130 --> 08:47.880
<b>Eliminate!</b>

08:55.720 --> 08:59.430
<b>The ultimate Imperial Relic 
has already been activated!</b>

08:59.430 --> 09:00.180
<b>Take this—</b>

09:00.640 --> 09:01.680
<b>Uh, ahem.</b>

09:03.640 --> 09:07.480
<b>The rebellion you sparked has 
thrown the empire into chaos!</b>

09:07.480 --> 09:09.440
<b>No! Listen to us!</b>

09:09.440 --> 09:12.110
<b>The empire has been in the grip of tyranny for many years.</b>

09:12.110 --> 09:15.530
<b>And this whole time, 
it is the weak who have suffered.</b>

09:16.200 --> 09:20.160
<b>No matter how much they hoped or prayed, 
no one ever came to help.</b>

09:20.830 --> 09:22.700
<b>Not even for Sayo and Ieyasu.</b>

09:22.700 --> 09:24.620
<b>They... They all died!</b>

09:26.080 --> 09:29.290
<b>A nation this cruel needs to change!</b>

09:29.290 --> 09:30.210
<b>Your Majesty,</b>

09:30.210 --> 09:34.090
<b>you mustn't be deceived by these words.</b>

09:34.090 --> 09:35.510
<b>Prime Minister Honest.</b>

09:35.510 --> 09:38.430
<b>It is <i>your</i> words that have been deceiving him!</b>

09:38.430 --> 09:39.930
<b>Oh?</b>

09:39.930 --> 09:43.850
<b>I don't appreciate these false accusations 
in front of the emperor.</b>

09:44.390 --> 09:47.060
<b>Everything I have advised him is out of love!</b>

09:47.060 --> 09:48.560
<b>Quit babbling.</b>

09:48.560 --> 09:50.980
<b>Can't you read the writing on the wall?</b>

09:50.980 --> 09:52.610
<b>This empire is finished!</b>

09:52.610 --> 09:54.110
<b>You brat.</b>

09:54.110 --> 09:56.030
<b>It's time you shut your mouth!</b>

09:56.030 --> 09:57.360
<b>Your Majesty,</b>

09:57.360 --> 10:00.570
<b>bring down the iron hammer of justice 
on these foolish rebels!</b>

10:00.950 --> 10:03.410
<b>I am the ruler of this nation!</b>

10:05.910 --> 10:07.040
<b>Wh-What's going on?</b>

10:10.960 --> 10:14.380
<b>The empire's trump card, Shikoutazer!{don't taze me shikou}</b>

10:14.380 --> 10:18.300
<b>Its strength rivals that of God!</b>

10:18.300 --> 10:20.680
<b>No, it <i>is</i> God!</b>

10:22.680 --> 10:28.310
<b>Those who betray the empire 
will be judged by God!</b>

10:28.310 --> 10:30.400
<b>Whoa, what's that?</b>

10:45.490 --> 10:46.870
<b>What the hell is that?</b>

10:46.870 --> 10:49.870
<b>That's the legendary Imperial Relic...</b>

10:50.960 --> 10:54.250
<b>Shikoutazer? It truly exists?</b>

10:54.250 --> 10:55.550
<b>That prime minister...</b>

10:55.550 --> 11:00.430
<b>So this is why he hasn't admitted defeat.</b>

11:02.260 --> 11:06.220
<b>Our empire has lasted generations by the grace and will of God.</b>

11:06.930 --> 11:11.190
<b>None can defy God!</b>

11:31.420 --> 11:34.130
<b>Stop!</b>

11:40.340 --> 11:42.260
<b>My, Your Majesty...</b>

11:42.260 --> 11:44.930
<b>You look every bit as valiant 
as an emperor should be.</b>

11:44.930 --> 11:49.680
<b>I'm sure your parents would be proud, if not for the unfortunate accident which claimed their lives.</b>

11:50.140 --> 11:51.140
<b>Yeah.</b>

11:51.140 --> 11:56.940
<b>Shikoutazer can only be used by those of the imperial bloodline.</b>

11:56.940 --> 12:03.240
<b>That said, you are without 
doubt the true emperor!</b>

12:03.240 --> 12:04.700
<b>That's right.</b>

12:04.700 --> 12:07.410
<b>I am the true heir.</b>

12:07.410 --> 12:08.660
<b>Now, Your Majesty...</b>

12:08.660 --> 12:10.370
<b>Without further ado!</b>

12:21.090 --> 12:22.840
<b>So this is what Stylish was talking about.</b>

12:22.840 --> 12:26.140
<b>The oldest and most powerful Imperial Relic.</b>

12:31.520 --> 12:34.480
<b>This... This is the right thing to do.</b>

12:34.900 --> 12:36.650
<b>Splendid!</b>

12:37.860 --> 12:40.990
<b>As long as we have this power, none can defy us.</b>

12:40.990 --> 12:42.400
<b>Everything will be ours.</b>

12:42.860 --> 12:46.870
<b><i>Let's turn a blind eye toward the destruction that's about to take place.</i></b>

12:46.870 --> 12:48.530
<b><i>It'll work out.</i></b>

12:48.530 --> 12:53.370
<b><i>We'll just have the ignorant citizens 
rebuild it again for the emperor and me!</i></b>

13:03.170 --> 13:04.380
<b><i>They're powerful.</i></b>

13:04.380 --> 13:06.220
<b><i>I'd expect no less from the emperor's personal guard.</i></b>

13:11.020 --> 13:12.060
<b><i>Tatsumi!</i></b>

13:12.060 --> 13:13.390
<b>Stop!</b>

13:13.390 --> 13:15.560
<b>How can you treat your own capital this way?</b>

13:15.560 --> 13:17.270
<b>Night Raid!</b>

13:17.270 --> 13:20.690
<b>It is time for you to reap what you have sown!</b>

13:23.570 --> 13:25.280
<b>How could you turn on your civilians?</b>

13:25.280 --> 13:26.820
<b>What kind of emperor are you?</b>

13:26.820 --> 13:28.070
<b>What the hell are you protecting?!</b>

13:28.070 --> 13:29.280
<b>Shut up!</b>

13:29.280 --> 13:31.660
<b>This empire's lasted for a thousand years.</b>

13:31.660 --> 13:34.410
<b>I can't let it end with me!</b>

13:34.410 --> 13:38.000
<b>Yes, yes! That's exactly right, Your Majesty!</b>

13:38.540 --> 13:40.750
<b>What does it matter how long it's lasted?</b>

13:41.920 --> 13:46.380
<b>From the day I was born, 
I've shouldered the future of this empire.</b>

13:48.180 --> 13:51.100
<b>How could you possibly understand how I feel?!</b>

13:51.100 --> 13:52.640
<b>I hope I never do!</b>

13:53.100 --> 13:57.230
<b>Do you know how many people are suffering at your hands?</b>

14:03.230 --> 14:06.900
<b>Look down, and see what you've wrought!</b>

14:19.790 --> 14:20.710
<b>Your Majesty!</b>

14:20.710 --> 14:22.630
<b>You cannot listen to him!</b>

14:22.630 --> 14:26.220
<b>If you let him sway you now, 
all we've done will be for naught!</b>

14:26.220 --> 14:28.970
<b>You must harden your heart!</b>

14:28.970 --> 14:31.600
<b>Th-That's right, isn't it...</b>

14:31.600 --> 14:34.010
<b>Don't avert your eyes, you fool!</b>

14:44.270 --> 14:45.860
<b>Your Majesty!</b>

14:50.320 --> 14:52.660
<b>If you have this much power,{staircase tl: this little power}</b>

14:52.660 --> 14:54.910
<b>turn it on the real evil!</b>

14:54.910 --> 14:55.830
<b>Shut up.</b>

14:56.160 --> 14:59.330
<b>Are you okay with being a puppet?!</b>

14:59.330 --> 15:02.290
<b>Shut the hell up!</b>

15:06.630 --> 15:07.880
<b>Wave!</b>

15:08.550 --> 15:10.090
<b>I am a soldier of the empire.</b>

15:10.630 --> 15:12.850
<b>I fight to protect the people!</b>

15:12.850 --> 15:14.470
<b>Glad to hear it!</b>

15:15.850 --> 15:18.980
<b>P-Plus, I owe you one.</b>

15:21.440 --> 15:23.060
<b>Huh? From when?</b>

15:23.060 --> 15:24.570
<b>Uh, never mind.</b>

15:25.110 --> 15:27.990
<b>Your Majesty, please calm yourself!</b>

15:27.990 --> 15:29.780
<b>This is a holy war!</b>

15:29.780 --> 15:32.450
<b>I can't turn back now!</b>

15:34.160 --> 15:35.990
<b>We'll stop him, no matter what it takes.</b>

15:35.990 --> 15:38.910
<b>We're the only ones who can.</b>

15:38.910 --> 15:41.170
<b>Yeah, you don't have to tell me twice.</b>

15:41.170 --> 15:42.290
<b>You...</b>

15:42.290 --> 15:45.290
<b>You would dare bare your fangs 
against the empire?</b>

15:45.290 --> 15:47.090
<b>Don't misunderstand!</b>

15:47.090 --> 15:49.630
<b>I haven't joined the rebel forces.</b>

15:49.630 --> 15:53.720
<b>But protecting the powerless is a soldier's duty!</b>

15:56.930 --> 15:58.600
<b>He's a real pain, too.</b>

15:59.100 --> 16:00.060
<b>Indeed.</b>

16:00.060 --> 16:00.810
<b>But...</b>

16:01.980 --> 16:03.690
<b>He's a pain we need.</b>

16:11.700 --> 16:12.910
<b>Hey, Wings.{"birdbrain" is probably a little too insulting}</b>

16:12.910 --> 16:14.200
<b>We'll settle our fight later.</b>

16:15.490 --> 16:16.990
<b>Not if I can help it.</b>

16:20.450 --> 16:21.290
<b>It's too hard!</b>

16:23.540 --> 16:25.750
<b>N-Not even Grand Chariot can break through!</b>

16:28.460 --> 16:31.010
<b><i>We can still fight!</i></b>

16:31.010 --> 16:32.340
<b><i>If we give up,</i></b>

16:32.340 --> 16:33.220
<b><i>it'll be over!</i></b>

16:42.810 --> 16:44.650
<b>Wh-What was that?</b>

16:44.650 --> 16:45.350
<b>Tatsumi!</b>

16:48.110 --> 16:50.860
<b><i>What did I just hit?</i></b>

16:51.240 --> 16:55.280
<b>No matter how sturdy something may appear, 
it will usually have a weakness.</b>

16:56.410 --> 16:59.790
<b>If you can discover that weakness in battle, 
it will help you greatly.</b>

16:59.790 --> 17:01.330
<b><i>Su...</i></b>

17:01.330 --> 17:02.410
<b>Wave!</b>

17:02.410 --> 17:03.790
<b>Make an opening for me!</b>

17:04.920 --> 17:05.620
<b>Okay!</b>

17:05.620 --> 17:08.130
<b>Your Majesty, pass judgment on the traitors!</b>

17:08.130 --> 17:11.840
<b>Th-Those who betray the empire</b>

17:11.840 --> 17:13.550
<b>are sentenced to death!</b>

17:28.940 --> 17:31.400
<b>This one area's showing signs of wear.</b>

17:31.400 --> 17:34.110
<b>The Relic must weigh an immense amount.</b>

17:34.110 --> 17:36.240
<b>Which means it's weakest 
where the load is concentrated!</b>

17:36.240 --> 17:37.110
<b>Right, Su?</b>

17:37.530 --> 17:39.450
<b>How dare you?!</b>

17:42.790 --> 17:43.790
<b>Tatsumi—</b>

17:52.380 --> 17:53.920
<b>Give up.</b>

17:53.920 --> 17:56.050
<b>Why must you continue to struggle?</b>

17:57.010 --> 17:59.970
<b>I'm begging you, give up!</b>

17:59.970 --> 18:01.760
<b>Don't underestimate me.</b>

18:01.760 --> 18:05.060
<b>I've weathered countless tragedies to get here.</b>

18:05.060 --> 18:06.440
<b>And as each of my comrades fell,</b>

18:06.440 --> 18:08.400
<b>I've carried their dreams and hopes with me!</b>

18:08.400 --> 18:12.900
<b>I won't let them down!</b>

18:17.740 --> 18:20.320
<b>You'll face lots of pain and despair on the way.</b>

18:20.320 --> 18:22.870
<b>In fact, the very road we walk is paved with tragedy.</b>

18:22.870 --> 18:26.910
<b>But we are the ones who chose to walk it.</b>

18:26.910 --> 18:28.120
<b><i>Bro...</i></b>

18:28.710 --> 18:30.880
<b>We'll take on the dirty work</b>

18:30.880 --> 18:33.340
<b>and bring about a new world.</b>

18:33.340 --> 18:36.090
<b>And once it's all over, we can disappear.</b>

18:36.090 --> 18:37.380
<b><i>Bro...</i></b>

18:37.380 --> 18:39.130
<b>Shout it out, Tatsumi!</b>

18:39.130 --> 18:41.350
<b>Fill it with your raging spirit!</b>

18:46.310 --> 18:50.060
<b>Incursio!</b>

18:54.360 --> 18:56.360
<b>Forged in ancient times,</b>

18:56.820 --> 18:58.360
<b>the armor that still evolves to this day...</b>

19:10.290 --> 19:11.960
<b>Don't come any closer...</b>

19:11.960 --> 19:16.510
<b>Don't come any closer!</b>

19:24.600 --> 19:26.470
<b>Fall!</b>

19:35.520 --> 19:37.030
<b>Tatsumi, you'll die!</b>

19:37.030 --> 19:38.900
<b>Like hell I will!</b>

19:38.900 --> 19:40.530
<b>I made a promise!</b>

19:48.540 --> 19:51.040
<b>I'm going to come back alive!</b>

19:51.040 --> 19:52.500
<b>Tatsumi!</b>

20:08.220 --> 20:09.140
<b>Tatsumi!</b>

20:58.480 --> 20:59.980
<b>I'm sorry.</b>

20:59.980 --> 21:02.990
<b>Looks like I'm gonna have 
to go back on my word.</b>

21:14.040 --> 21:16.040
<b>You promised me!</b>

21:16.040 --> 21:18.340
<b>You said you'd come back alive!</b>

21:19.040 --> 21:20.250
<b>Tatsumi...</b>

21:28.930 --> 21:30.560
<b>Is it over?</b>

21:34.600 --> 21:36.270
<b>Did we lose?</b>

21:36.770 --> 21:38.480
<b>Did the empire—</b>

21:38.480 --> 21:39.480
<b>did I—</b>

21:40.230 --> 21:42.070
<b>lose?</b>

21:47.990 --> 21:49.990
<b>Tatsumi's...</b>

21:49.990 --> 21:51.490
<b>dead.</b>

